              | Ifs of Exp * Block * Block
              | Assign of Name.t * Exp
              | AssignArr of Name.t * Exp * Exp
              | Decl of Name.t * Exp option
              | Nop
              | Free of Name.t
              | Ret of Exp
              | Halt of string
